code>isSupported()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/lookupNamespaceURI\"><code>lookupNamespaceURI()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/lookupPrefix\"><code>lookupPrefix()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/normalize\"><code>normalize()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/removeChild\"><code>removeChild()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/replaceChild\"><code>replaceChild()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Vererbung:</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"allgemein","title":"Allgemein","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Gibt das Elternelement des gegebenen Datenknotens, entsprechend des DOM-Baums zurück.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">elternelement = node.parentNode\n</pre>\n<p><code><var>elternelement</var></code> enthält das Elternelement des gegebenen Datenknotens.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiel","title":"Beispiel","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:javascript notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> dokument <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>documentElement<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>parentNode<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"anmerkungen","title":"Anmerkungen","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Es kann sich bei dem Elternelement um ein <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a>, ein <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a> oder ein <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a> handeln.</li>\n <li><code>parentNode</code> gibt <code>null</code> zurück bei folgenden Knotentypen: <code>Attr</code>, <code>Document</code>, <code>DocumentFragment</code>, <code>Entity</code>, and <code>Notation</code>.</li>\n <li>Außerdem wird <code>null</code> zurückgegeben, wenn der Knoten bisher nicht an den DOM-Baum angefügt wurde (weil er womöglich gerade erst erstellt wurde).</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/firstChild\"><code>Node.firstChild</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/lastChild\"><code>Node.lastChild</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/childNodes\"><code>Node.childNodes</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/nextSibling\"><code>Node.nextSibling</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/previousSibling\"><code>Node.previousSibling</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browserunterstützung","title":"Browserunterstützung","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Wir konvertieren die Kompatibilitätsdaten in ein maschinenlesbares JSON Format</a></strong>.\n            Diese Kompatibilitätstabelle liegt noch im alten Format vor,\n            denn die darin enthaltenen Daten wurden noch nicht konvertiert.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Finde heraus wie du helfen kannst! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect2\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Mobile</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n <table class=\"compat-table\">\n  <tbody>\n   <tr>\n    <th>Feature</th>\n    <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n    <th>Chrome</th>\n    <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n    <th>Opera</th>\n    <th>Safari</th>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td>Basic support</td>\n    <td>1.0 (1.7 oder früher)</td>\n    <td>0.2</td>\n    <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   </tr>\n  </tbody>\n </table>\n</div>\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n <table class=\"compat-table\">\n  <tbody>\n   <tr>\n    <th>Feature</th>\n    <th>Android</th>\n    <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n    <th>IE Mobile</th>\n    <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n    <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td>Basic support</td>\n    <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n    <td>1.0 (1)</td>\n    <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   </tr>\n  </tbody>\n </table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikation","title":"Spezifikation","isH3":false,"content":"<p><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Core/core.html#ID-1060184317\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM Level 2 Core: Node.parentNode</a> (en)</p>\n<p></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Allgemein","id":"allgemein"},{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Beispiel","id":"beispiel"},{"text":"Anmerkungen","id":"anmerkungen"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"},{"text":"Browserunterstützung","id":"browserunterstützung"},{"text":"Spezifikation","id":"spezifikation"}],"summary":"Gibt das Elternelement des gegebenen Datenknotens, entsprechend des DOM-Baums zurück.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Node.parentNode","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Node.parentNode","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"element.parentNode","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Node.parentNode","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"element.parentNode","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Node.parentNode","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Node.parentNode","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Node.parentNode","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/node/parentnode","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/node/parentnode/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Node","title":"Node"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/parentNode","title":"Node.parentNode"}],"pageTitle":"Node.parentNode - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}